title: García Stresses Importance of Diverse Faculty (California State University, Fullerton)
text: ( Source : California State University, Fullerton ) Cal State Fullerton President Mildred García discussed the current state of and successful strategies for increasing faculty diversity on college campuses in her Oct. 13 keynote presentation,
